<topic id='dataset_national_cancer_waiting_times_monitoring_data_set.overview'>
  <title>Overview</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Set: National Cancer Waiting Times Monitoring Data Set - Overview</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <b>Introduction</b>
      </p>
      <p>
The information in the 
              <xref outputclass="dataSet"
               keyref="dataset_national_cancer_waiting_times_monitoring_data_set">National Cancer Waiting Times Monitoring Data Set</xref>
 is required to provide details on cancer 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICES</xref>
 in England. This enables the performance monitoring of 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_health_care_provider">Health Care Providers</xref>
 and 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">Clinical Commissioning Groups</xref>
 in order to maintain and increase standards across England.        </p>
      <p>Cancer Waiting Times data relates to the waiting time requirements outlined in the:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/+/www.dh.gov.uk/en/Publicationsandstatistics/Publications/PublicationsPolicyandGuidance/DH_4009609"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">'NHS Cancer Plan (2000)'</xref>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/+/www.dh.gov.uk/en/Healthcare/Cancer/DH_091120"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">'Cancer Reform Strategy (2007)'</xref>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/the-national-cancer-strategy"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">'Improving Outcomes: A Strategy for Cancer (2011)'</xref>
               <p> and</p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/cancer-strategy.pdf"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">'Achieving World-Class Cancer Outcomes: Taking the strategy forward (2016)'</xref>
               <p>.</p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="dataSet"
               keyref="dataset_national_cancer_waiting_times_monitoring_data_set">National Cancer Waiting Times Monitoring Data Set</xref>
 supports waiting times which are defined on the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/data-and-information/data-collections-and-data-sets/data-collections/cancerwaitingtimescwt"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Cancer Waiting Times Data Collection (CWT)</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <b>Patient Pathway Scenarios</b>
      </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_national_cancer_waiting_times_monitoring_data_set_scenarios">Patient Pathway Scenarios</xref>
 for the 
              <xref outputclass="dataSet"
               keyref="dataset_national_cancer_waiting_times_monitoring_data_set">National Cancer Waiting Times Monitoring Data Set</xref>
 are to be used to manage the collection of data for all 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 suspected of having, or diagnosed with cancer.        </p>
      <p>
         <b>Transmission</b>
      </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>Data can be transmitted to the Cancer Waiting Times System through any of three routes:</p>
            </div>
            <ul>
               <li>
                  <div>
                     <p>Bulk upload via an XML file</p>
                  </div>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <div>
                     <p>Bulk upload via a CSV file</p>
                  </div>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <div>
                     <p>Single record entry through the Cancer Waiting Times Submission portal</p>
                  </div>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
The specification for CSV upload file is detailed in the 
                                <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/data-and-information/data-collections-and-data-sets/data-collections/cancerwaitingtimescwt"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">'National Cancer Waiting Times User Manual'</xref>
 available on the 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
Data for XML submission will be formatted into an XML file as per 
                                <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                        keyref="supporting_definition_technology_reference_data_update_distribution__trud_">Technology Reference Data Update Distribution (TRUD)</xref>
 at: 
                                <xref href="https://isd.hscic.gov.uk/trud3/user/authenticated/group/101/pack/36"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">NHS Data Model and Dictionary: DD XML Schemas</xref>
               </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
Once data is transmitted to the Cancer Waiting Times system it will undergo further validation. Details of this validation is available on the 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website at: 
                                <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/data-and-information/data-collections-and-data-sets/data-collections/cancerwaitingtimescwt"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">Cancer Waiting Times</xref>.                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
         <b>Further guidance</b>
      </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
Further guidance relating to the 
                                <xref outputclass="dataSet"
                        keyref="dataset_national_cancer_waiting_times_monitoring_data_set">National Cancer Waiting Times Monitoring Data Set</xref>
 is available on the 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website at: 
                                <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/data-and-information/data-collections-and-data-sets/data-collections/cancerwaitingtimescwt"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">Cancer Waiting Times</xref>.                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
Queries regarding the 
                                <xref outputclass="dataSet"
                        keyref="dataset_national_cancer_waiting_times_monitoring_data_set">National Cancer Waiting Times Monitoring Data Set</xref>
 should be addressed to 
                                <xref href="mailto:england.cancerwaitsdata@nhs.net"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">england.cancerwaitsdata@nhs.net</xref>.                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
See 
              <b>
            <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                  keyref="supporting_definition_national_cancer_waiting_times_monitoring_data_set_scenarios">Patient Pathway Scenarios</xref>
         </b>, for the scenarios which show:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <p>the data items required for a range of health care scenarios and</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>information on how records will be validated to ensure these scenarios have been correctly reported.</p>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
         <b>Mandation</b>
      </p>
      <p>The Mandation column indicates the recommendation for the inclusion of data.</p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>M = Mandatory: this data element is mandatory and the technical process (e.g. submission of the data set, production of output etc) cannot be completed without this data element being present</p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
R = Required: NHS business processes cannot be delivered without this data element.  Required data elements may not be applicable to all 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient_pathway">PATIENT PATHWAYS</xref>, see 
                                <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                        keyref="supporting_definition_national_cancer_waiting_times_monitoring_data_set_scenarios">Patient Pathway Scenarios</xref>
 for further details                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>O = Optional: the inclusion of this data element is optional as required for local purposes.</p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
         <b>Data Set Constraints</b>
      </p>
      <p>
For guidance on the Data Set constraints, see the 
              <xref outputclass="xmlSchemaConstraint"
               keyref="xml_schema_constraint_national_cancer_waiting_times_monitoring_data_set_constraints">National Cancer Waiting Times Monitoring Data Set Constraints</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <b>XML Schema</b>
      </p>
      <p>
For guidance on downloading the XML Schema, see 
              <xref href="https://v3.datadictionary.nhs.uk/data_dictionary/messages/xml_schema_trud_download.html"
               scope="external"
               format="html">XML_Schema_TRUD_Download</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
